name: Birds on a Wire
description:
3 piece set!!!

Birds on a Wire shorts, top, and shoes. All items are preshrunk so you have no worries about them drawing up in the wash. Items are machine washable and can be put in the dryer.

Substitute pants for the shorts at no extra cost!
Substitute shirt for the onsie at no extra cost!

Please send a message when ordering indicating the size you would like the shorts, top, and shoes (newborn, 3 months, 6 months, 9 months, or 12 months).

name: Classic Americana Shorts and Shoes
description:
Dress your baby in style! Red gingham shorts pair nicely with chambray shoes lined in the same red gingham. Pair this set up with a polo shirt for a classic summertime look. 

Items have been pre-shrunk so you have no worries about them drawing up in the wash. Items are machine washable and can go in the dryer.

Set is also available in navy and green gingham.

Please send a message when ordering indicating the size and color you would like. (Newborn, 3 months, 6 months, 9 months, or 12 months)
